name: the fountain of the music
description:
from collection: "outside: music"

You close your eyes
Drowning
Music flows inside you
And the musician with his disheveled hair 
sinks into his instrument
The strings are shaking
Music flows from your ears to your heart
River of Notes
Roaring
Sound drops
spills on your face
on your heart
Everything is smoked in cigarette smoke
but this moment
Everything but
The source of the music
And the musician plays music with strands of his hair
as his guitar strings

for my brother, 
 and all the fountains of the music
